# Secrets only. Copy to `.env` beside your document (loaded automatically) and
# fill in. `.env` is gitignored — keep nothing here that you'd commit.
#
# Non-secret config (fps, viewport, …), voiceover defaults (provider/voice/model),
# and shared variables now live in a committed `recordable.config.json` — see
# `recordable.config.example.json`. This file is for secrets only.

# ── Voiceover credential ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ElevenLabs API key, required for real synthesis. (`mock` provider needs no key —
# set it in recordable.config.json's `voiceover` block or a document's frontmatter.)
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# ── Secret variables (VAR_ prefix) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Reference with {{ name }} in any action string arg or in Markdown narration.
# Names are case- and separator-insensitive: VAR_ADMIN_PASSWORD ≡ {{adminPassword}}
# ≡ {{admin_password}}. Non-secret variables go in recordable.config.json instead.
# VAR_ADMIN_PASSWORD=
